snippet: The mystery package at the center of a UK Anti-Doping investigation into British Cycling contained a flu treatment, Team Sky chief Dave Brailsford told Members of Parliament on Monday....
lead_paragraph: The mystery package at the center of a UK Anti-Doping investigation into British Cycling contained a flu treatment, Team Sky chief Dave Brailsford told Members of Parliament on Monday.

headline.main: Cycling: Mystery Package Was Flu Treatment, Says Team Sky Boss Brailsford
